{"tid":2110804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"認人有疑點 雷射筆襲警案被告脫罪","createTime":"2020-07-16T06:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T07:14:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed4637741b272b1efa24e02de08357ebc473926","tid":2110804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:59:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/4VVZKRFETF3AG6QHW2PKRC3DPM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2F4VVZKRFETF3AG6QHW2PKRC3DPM%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n32WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=490b2551\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2F4VVZKRFETF3AG6QHW2PKRC3DPM%2F&h=93930696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/4VVZKRFETF3AG6QHW2PKRC3DPM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n認人有疑點 雷射筆襲警案被告脫罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7JKRIjfwoGZYxZfLzjrdktPAEsk=/640x490/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3KVLJ4WQZ5RURGTOSPK7OAZLLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7JKRIjfwoGZYxZfLzjrdktPAEsk%3D%2F640x490%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3KVLJ4WQZ5RURGTOSPK7OAZLLM.jpg&h=75a0641d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告林澤光（右）獲判兩罪名均不成立。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】示威者去年12月15日在旺角聚集，一名抹車工被指以雷射筆射向警車、光束透過玻璃射到車內警長的瞳孔兩秒，被控襲警及管有攻擊性武器罪受審。案件昨裁決，裁判官黃士翔認為聲稱遇襲的警長沒認出男子容貌，單憑衣飾及所在位置認人，但法庭不能肯定被告就是施襲者；加上呈堂雷射筆沒放入防干擾證物袋內，證物鏈有問題。黃官又指搜出雷射筆亦不足證明其傷人意圖，裁定被告兩項罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。因案件在身時須每晚6時至翌晨3時宵禁，影響生活，其間時常失眠。他寄語香港人：「要堅持，唔好放棄，每件事都可能出現奇蹟。」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。裁判官稱有些證人對某些事自認堅實無疑，但亦可能犯錯。警長雖自言下車時該男子只離開他視線一秒，但他需從副駕駛座轉身、推車門、下車，以及將視線重新放在人群找上該男子，過程至少如辯方所提出的三至五秒長。<br />\n<br />\n此外，警長明言沒。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證物放普通膠袋 或曾受干擾<br />\n<br />\n裁判官續指，呈堂雷射筆只是放在普通膠袋而非防干擾證物袋，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC4604/19"},{"pid":"c6dc53f77e9dfffc1a33ae20487ec75550da968a","tid":2110804,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"警員冇講「視線冇離開過被告」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f98c05f2b043016286bc6ac59a87cafe90d6cd","tid":2110804,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3e72ea421f8a439c0c96463df095871ffb5e50","tid":2110804,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"個官好快唔會再審呢類案"}]}